CONJURE ELEMENTAL

Usage       : cast 'conjure elemental' [elemental type]
Accumulative: -
Duration    : 48 hours.

Casting this spell will call upon one of the world's elementals to be brought
forth to do your bidding for a period of 48 hours.  Conjuring requires
a stone to be held, and the stone is sacrificed in the casting of the spell.

red stone for fire elementals
pale blue stone for water elementals
grey stone for earth elementals
clear stone for air elementals

See Also: CREATE GOLEM, MONSUM, CACAODEMON, CHARM MONSTER
Related Topics: SPELL INFO
